<h2 style="margin: 0 0 16px; color: #0f172a;">Order Confirmation</h2>

<p style="margin: 0 0 12px;">Hi {{name}},</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">
  We received your order <strong>{{orderNumber}}</strong> and are preparing it now.
</p>

<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="width: 100%; margin: 0 0 16px; border-collapse: collapse;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #475569; width: 140px;">Order Number</td>
    <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>{{orderNumber}}</strong></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #475569;">Total Amount</td>
    <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>{{orderDetails.totalAmount}}</strong></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #475569;">Shipping Address</td>
    <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{orderDetails.shippingAddress}}</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin: 0; color: #475569;">
  We will notify you again once your order is shipped.
</p>
